Factors in automation

 Business issues such as flexibility and fit with 
strategy
 Operational issues such as repeatability and precision 
and effect on performance drivers such as time to 
market (e.g Pharmaceutical)
 Regulatory issues
 Social issues such as technological environment and 
workforce implications
 Labor costs
 Sources of improvement and performance drivers

