Standardization factors

 Product standardization (does it vary by 
market)
 Stability of technology (do new technologies 
leapfrog or evolve)
 Basis for learning (technology or worker 
based)
 Levels of volume (eg cars in Brazil)
 Ranges of technologies and impact of labor 
(can you use manual at low volumes)

